OL,3,CMan charged with criminal damage after
OL,4,CChurchill statue defaced with graffiti
OL,6,FA 38-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith criminal damage after graffiti
OL,8,Fwas sprayed on the statue of Sir
OL,9,FWinston Churchill in Westminster,
OL,10,Fbranding the former prime minister a
OL,11,F"Zionist war criminal".
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police said Caspar
OL,14,FSan Giorgio, of no fixed address, was
OL,15,Farrested shortly after 4am on Friday.
OL,17,FHe was taken into custody and charged
OL,18,Fjust before 4am on Saturday.
