OL,3,CMan charged with criminal damage after
OL,4,CChurchill statue defaced with graffiti
OL,6,FPolice said he is due to appear at
OL,7,FHighbury Corner Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FSaturday morning.
OL,10,FThe bronze statue, in Parliament
OL,11,FSquare, opposite the Houses of
OL,12,FParliament, was defaced with phrases
OL,13,Fincluding "Stop the Genocide" and
OL,14,F"Free Palestine" sprayed in red paint.
OL,16,FFurther graffiti read "Never again is
OL,17,FNow" and "Globalise the Intifada".
